          <source>In the <ph id="ph1">&lt;xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView&gt;</ph> control, the <ph id="ph2">&lt;xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.AllowUserToOrderColumns%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType&gt;</ph> property value determines whether users can move columns to different positions.</source>
